## Implementation Order

1. `users` â†’ `vehicles` â†’ `pricing_rules`
2. `rental_records` (depends on users, vehicles, pricing_rules)
3. `fleet_vehicle_assignments` (depends on users, vehicles)
4. `maintenance_logs` (depends on users, vehicles)
5. `notifications` (depends on users)
